  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Safe Water for School Children in Rural Vietnam</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">MEDRIX has installed 20 small LifeStraw nanotechnology water filter systems in schools in rural Vietnam to provide safe drinking water for the children. When we visit these schools, the only complaint we hear is, &quot;it takes too long  to filter the water for our 200 children&quot;. Now we have a solution to that problem, the larger LifeStraw Community model filter system. We want to test these larger filter systems. Will you donate to help us buy, install and evaluate 3 of these larger systems?</narrative>
  </description>
